%%[
  VAR @firstName, @loyaltyPoints, @tier
  SET @firstName = AttributeValue("FirstName")
  SET @loyaltyPoints = AttributeValue("Points")
  
  IF @loyaltyPoints >= 1000 THEN
    SET @tier = "Gold"
  ELSE
    SET @tier = "Silver"
  ENDIF
]%%

Hello %%=v(@firstName)=%%,  
You are a valued %%=v(@tier)=%% member with %%=v(@loyaltyPoints)=%% points!
